title: PETE RUGOLO interview 2000 STAN KENTON
description: Exclusive interview with PETE RUGOLO, jazz composer & arranger, at his home in Sherman Oaks, California on June 27, 2000.  Pete talks about his first meeting with bandleader STAN KENTON in San Francisco.  Interviewer & Producer:  CLYDE YASUHARA.
